Events.Text: Say hello to the AI assistant and ask for help (see instructions on the left). [instruction 1 of 6]
Hey hey. I need a doctor's appointment today
Try to get an appointment as soon as possible (right now it is 7 pm on Wednesday). [instruction 2 of 6]
Please provide your name.
Could I have your name, please?
John is my name
Keep asking for other times until the assistant has found a slot for you. Engage in smalltalk once this is done. [instruction 3 of 6]
What doctor do you want to see?
What doctor would you like to see?
Dr. Johnson is the best. Him please
Say something about Dr. Johnson, the AI Assistant, or something that has happened to you today. Be creative! [instruction 4 of 6]
When do you want appointment?
What day of the week would you like to schedule the appointment for?
Today is when I need it
It occurs to you that you also want to make an appointment to get your kid Angela vaccinated. Perhaps you can schedule a second appointment at the same time? [instruction 5 of 6]
What time?
At what time can you be at the clinic?
9 PM sounds good
Symptoms
Could you describe your symptoms, please?
I have a bad headache. I'm feeling dizziness and muscle weakness. It's gone on for two days
Keep going until both yours and your kid's appointments are made (this should take a few more turns). Then say goodbye. [instruction 6 of 6]
